2026-05-10T03:29:43.7532911Z 22    <!--
2026-05-10T03:29:43.7533651Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-10T03:29:43.7534547Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-10T03:29:43.7535396Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-10T03:29:43.7536403Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-10T03:29:43.7537579Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-10T03:29:43.7538616Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-10T03:29:43.7539617Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-10T03:29:43.7540617Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-10T03:29:43.7541590Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-10T03:29:43.7542538Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-10T03:29:43.7543304Z 33    -->
2026-05-10T03:29:43.7544094Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
