2026-05-10T03:29:44.1528568Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-10T03:29:44.1528887Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-10T03:29:44.1529396Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-10T03:29:44.1529731Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-10T03:29:44.1530059Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-10T03:29:44.1530348Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-10T03:29:44.1530503Z 32    -->
